🛠️ How to Add publish Script
Open your package.json file and in the "scripts" section, add this line:

json
Copy
Edit
"publish": "npm run build && npm run preview"
✅ Example scripts section after update:
json
Copy
Edit
"scripts": {
  "dev": "vite",
  "build": "vite build",
  "preview": "vite preview",
  "publish": "npm run build && npm run preview"
}
🚀 To use it:
In your terminal, run:

bash
Copy
Edit
npm run publish
It will:

Run vite build to generate your /dist

Run vite preview to serve the build locally for testing before deploying











